commit_list.message:
[CD/PL][73483944] Limit numbers on map requests

For miles and the various latitudes and longitudes, limit their scale to
4 digits after the decimal point. In apps like AG, this should help
caching, since there should be less variation in similar requests.

[CD][73483944] Round miles to nearest integer

Instead of limiting the scale of miles to 4 digits after the decimal
place like we do for latitude and longitude, round miles to the nearest
integer.

Also adds some flexibility to the limitScaleOf function so that a limit
other than 4 can be specified.
